<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="this-adj">this <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ðɪs/    美 /ðɪs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>这个；以下的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Get out of this room.
离开这个房间。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They wanted to show us this point: She is innocent.
他们想告诉我们以下观点：她是无辜的。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>this evening / year
今晚/今年</p></div></div>